<li class='cover' id='bookCover_55346809'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/55346809-safe-word"><img alt="Safe Word" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1600202428l/55346809._SX98_.jpg" />
